title: The Mars Colony is Never Gonna Happen: Outer Space is Bunk.
description: I grew up being taught a lot of lies about space exploration and the future of humanity's place in the solar system/galaxy.  Really, I had to learn that much of what I was taught as "science" (in this respect) was just as much a fable as hearing about elves or yetis in the forest, etc.
